channel.title: Own source
channel.description:
hey i really want to know how to make my own source...
I want to make it fast training.. but not too fast.. i want it to have a 1hit weapon like a mouse toy or something.. and i want the home to be like v0id-pkz's.. please tell me how to do these.. if u don't know how to either just tell me how to make my own source and how to change the home location and stuff..

item.title: Own source
item.dc:creator: @Treber Treber
item.description:
@Treber wrote:

Download a source. To make your training fast, make all your XP rate’s like 2000 or 3000. To make a weapon 1 hit, you have to edit the bonuses in item.cfg.

Changing home location is usually in player.java or client.java.

It’s nearly impossible to make your own source from scratch unless you’re an experienced programmer and know what you’re during 100%.

Read full topic
